data.description: Welcome to an oasis in Mira Loma Estates in Sacramento. This 4bedroom/2.5bathroom home has it all! Pull up to an expansive front yard with new sprinkler system, grass, and cement featuring an oversized driveway. Walk through the double doors into almost 2,000 square feet single story home. Living room boasts wall to wall brick fireplace with mantle. The kitchen/dining room combo is perfect for entertaining. Kitchen features granite countertops, farmhouse sink, stainless steel appliances, and pull out drawer cabinets. Large dining area can fit an oversized table. Second fireplace makes for cozy dinners by the fire. Enter through the barn door to a half bathroom and laundry room with upper cabinets. The rest of the home features 3 good sized bedrooms and hallway bathroom along with the primary suite at the end of the hall. Dual paned windows throughout house. Original beautiful hardwood floors. Walk outside to an oasis of a backyard including sparkling pool, new sod, iconic oak tree, fruit trees, and plenty of space!
